34:00.790 --> 34:02.150
- Was this the first time?

34:03.820 --> 34:05.390
- No.

34:05.390 --> 34:07.190
- May we approach, your honor?

34:11.060 --> 34:13.060
In light of the people's
failure to disclose

34:13.060 --> 34:15.030
the romantic relationship
between this witness

34:15.030 --> 34:16.170
and the victim,

34:16.170 --> 34:19.230
I move to exclude
all of her testimony.

34:19.239 --> 34:21.400
- First of all, we know
of no romantic relationship.

34:21.409 --> 34:27.080
I'm ready to put the bartender
from Sheridan's on the stand.

34:27.080 --> 34:29.239
I'm sure she told you
exactly what she told me.

34:30.449 --> 34:32.210
- Which is?

34:32.219 --> 34:34.449
- The first thing the witness
said to judge Kinzie was,

34:34.449 --> 34:37.889
and I quote,
"did you tell her yet?"

34:39.020 --> 34:42.219
You don't have to be married
to know what that means.

34:42.230 --> 34:44.360
- The jury can consider
this evidence.

34:44.360 --> 34:45.429
- Thank you, your honor.

34:45.429 --> 34:47.360
- Don't thank me yet, Mr. stone.

34:47.360 --> 34:50.230
You can expect
an instruction so harsh

34:50.230 --> 34:53.370
that the jury will disregard
Ms. Valdez's testimony

34:53.370 --> 34:55.469
on their own.

35:20.200 --> 35:21.430
Valdez.

35:23.400 --> 35:25.200
Send her up.

35:28.200 --> 35:31.340
- Thank you for seeing me.

35:31.340 --> 35:34.410
My friend told me what
happened in court today.

35:35.950 --> 35:37.910
I want to apologize
if I caused you...

35:37.920 --> 35:40.880
- I'm fine.

35:40.890 --> 35:42.950
- It never ends.

35:42.950 --> 35:46.220
- I'm so sorry you have
to go through this again.

35:46.220 --> 35:49.360
- Everyone thinks I
should hate judge Kinzie.

35:49.360 --> 35:52.090
But the truth is,

35:52.100 --> 35:55.630
Stan Kendricks getting
such a short sentence...

35:55.630 --> 35:58.230
It was my fault.

35:58.240 --> 36:00.140
- No, it wasn't, Zoe.

36:00.140 --> 36:03.310
- I met with the probation
officer prior to sentencing.

36:03.310 --> 36:06.210
She asked me what I wanted.

36:06.210 --> 36:08.940
After living through
the nightmare

36:08.950 --> 36:11.150
and re-living it
in the courtroom,

36:11.150 --> 36:13.380
I still...

36:13.380 --> 36:16.050
I know this sounds weird,

36:16.050 --> 36:19.420
but I still felt sorry for Stan.

36:21.120 --> 36:23.160
It's crazy, but I felt like...

36:23.160 --> 36:26.130
I was going to ruin
Stan's whole life

36:26.130 --> 36:28.060
because he made
one stupid mistake.

36:30.200 --> 36:33.440
That went into
the P.O.'S report.

36:33.440 --> 36:36.410
Judge Kinzie
just did what I asked.

36:38.010 --> 36:39.410
- Wow.

36:41.340 --> 36:44.450
- I know.
I am stupid.

36:44.450 --> 36:48.280
After lots of therapy,
I realized just how stupid.

36:48.290 --> 36:50.490
I should've paid for that,
not judge Kinzie.

36:52.360 --> 36:55.060
- You are not responsible
for what Jon did.

37:00.430 --> 37:02.460
- I've taken enough
of your time.

37:04.330 --> 37:06.440
I should be the happiest
girl on the planet...

37:06.440 --> 37:09.170
Starting a new chapter
in my life with my fiancé.

37:09.170 --> 37:13.180
- I didn't want Blake
to get dragged into this mess.

37:13.180 --> 37:16.980
I mean, he knows, but...

37:24.450 --> 37:27.520
- Off the record?

37:27.520 --> 37:29.260
- Yeah, come in.

37:29.260 --> 37:31.160
I probably lost the case anyway.

37:34.400 --> 37:36.200
- I don't know
if I ever said it,

37:36.200 --> 37:38.530
but I am sorry about Kinzie.

37:44.240 --> 37:47.410
- This is exactly what
ray dreaded most...

37:47.410 --> 37:49.510
A case in which the law
gets in the way of justice.

37:51.050 --> 37:54.380
- Like a five-month
sentence for a rape?

37:54.390 --> 37:56.350
- He was just following
the probation officer's

37:56.350 --> 37:57.490
Presentencing report.

37:57.490 --> 38:00.290
- Martha Stewart
served more time.

38:00.290 --> 38:03.230
- And Teddy Kennedy
never served a day.

38:04.360 --> 38:06.090
- Touché.

38:08.160 --> 38:09.300
- If I learned one thing
from Zoe,

38:09.300 --> 38:10.600
it's to focus on the future.

38:10.600 --> 38:13.300
After all this,
she's getting married.

38:23.110 --> 38:25.380
Good luck in court tomorrow.

38:25.380 --> 38:27.120
- Thank you.

38:31.490 --> 38:34.390
- Can I ask?

38:34.390 --> 38:36.460
- Something Dr. Charles told me.

38:55.450 --> 38:57.850
- Mr. stone.

38:57.850 --> 39:00.520
I'd like you to meet Blake,
my fiancé.

39:00.520 --> 39:02.150
- It's nice to meet you.

39:02.150 --> 39:04.220
It's very kind of you
to come out and support Zoe.

39:04.220 --> 39:05.450
- I love her.
It's the least I could do.

39:05.460 --> 39:07.520
- Uh, when are you
getting married?

39:07.520 --> 39:09.290
- This summer.

39:09.290 --> 39:10.430
- And it's a big wedding?

39:10.430 --> 39:12.360
- All our friends will be there.

39:14.460 --> 39:16.400
- How could you bring him here?

39:16.400 --> 39:18.500
- Sit down, Jon.

39:20.200 --> 39:22.200
- I moved on, Jon.

39:22.210 --> 39:25.440
<i>You</i> moved on.

39:25.440 --> 39:27.510
Kendricks moved on.
- Jon...

39:27.510 --> 39:31.310
- Everybody moved on!
- Jon!

39:31.320 --> 39:34.480
Stop it.
- Everybody moved on but me!

39:34.490 --> 39:35.580
- Is that why you
killed the judge?

39:35.590 --> 39:37.490
- You're damn right it is!

39:51.130 --> 39:53.240
- We should talk.

39:59.610 --> 40:02.180
It's over, Jon.

40:05.450 --> 40:07.550
- How did that happen?

40:07.550 --> 40:09.380
- Zoe announced her engagement
on Facebook

40:09.390 --> 40:12.150
a few days before
Jon killed judge Kinzie.

40:12.160 --> 40:14.260
That's what triggered him.

40:16.160 --> 40:18.460
- I can't believe
he agreed to 30 years.

40:18.460 --> 40:20.560
- A courtroom full of people
heard him confess.

40:33.640 --> 40:36.180
- Let me ask you this.

40:36.180 --> 40:37.650
If I told you I wasn't
sleeping with ray,

40:37.650 --> 40:40.550
would you have believed me?

40:45.290 --> 40:47.190
- I don't know.

40:47.190 --> 40:50.490
Maybe skepticism is some
sort of evolutionary shield

40:50.490 --> 40:52.590
that helps the species survive.

40:53.660 --> 40:55.500
The truth is,
if I flat-out said

40:55.500 --> 40:59.570
there's no way I would
ever sleep with ray,

40:59.570 --> 41:03.210
it wouldn't have changed
your investigation one bit.

41:03.210 --> 41:05.410
We are all endowed
by our creator

41:05.410 --> 41:07.540
with unalienable rights.

41:07.540 --> 41:11.280
I recall reading that
in some old document.

41:11.280 --> 41:15.250
Is the right to be respected
by your fellow man.

41:17.220 --> 41:20.690
If my relationship with ray,
whatever it was,

41:20.690 --> 41:23.260
would've helped you catch
or convict his killer,

41:23.260 --> 41:24.690
I would've told you.

41:24.700 --> 41:29.000
But because I knew it didn't,
I figured I'd rely on...

41:29.000 --> 41:31.500
Another right referenced
in that dusty old document.

41:38.510 --> 41:40.610
- Privacy.
